{"analytics_identifier":"AG1407","base_path":"/government/organisations/the-queen-elizabeth-memorial-committee","content_id":"1e4225ef-6beb-4d04-ab94-f9d9b39802d5","description":"The Queen Elizabeth Memorial Committee is a joint body set up to advise the Government and the Royal Household on the national memorialisation of Her late Majesty Queen Elizabeth II QEMC is an ad-hoc advisory group of the Cabinet Office .","details":{"acronym":"QEMC","alternative_format_contact_email":"queenelizabethmemorial@cabinetoffice.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Queen Elizabeth Memorial Committee is a joint body set up to advise the Government and the Royal Household on the national memorialisation of Her late Majesty Queen Elizabeth II</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"The Queen Elizabeth Memorial Committee\">QEMC</abbr> is an ad-hoc advisory group of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"cabinet-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"The Queen Elizabeth Memorial Committee"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/the-queen-elizabeth-memorial-committee/about/terms-of-reference","title":"Terms of reference"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/final-recommendations-for-the-national-memorial-to-queen-elizabeth-ii-announced-to-coincide-with-the-centenary-of-her-birth","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e8f4fe08ecdb5c6f34ae3c/s712_Image_1.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e8f4fed36883a64473b860/s465_Image_1.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e8f4fe606c20d41216328e/Image_1.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-20T22:30:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The recommendations made by the Queen Elizabeth Memorial Committee, including the masterplan for a permanent memorial in St James’s Park, London, a new charitable trust for regenerating community assets across the United Kingdom, and an online Digital Memorial to allow people to submit their own memories of the late Queen, have been announced.</p>\n</div>","title":"Final Recommendations for the national memorial to Queen Elizabeth II announced to coincide with the centenary of her birth"},{"document_type":"Independent report","href":"/government/publications/final-recommendations-for-the-memorial-to-queen-elizabeth","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e8e830d36883a64473b858/s712_Image.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e8e830ed93f72cf8163288/s465_Image.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e8e830ed93f72cf8163287/Image.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-22T16:21:54.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Queen Elizabeth Memorial Committee has announced its final recommendations for a permanent national memorial to Queen Elizabeth II, to coincide with the centenary of her birth.</p>\n</div>","title":"Final recommendations for the memorial to Queen Elizabeth"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/a-garden-for-the-commonwealth-the-landscape-vision-for-the-queen-elizabeth-ii-memorial","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69aebe0cc78869bf8eb8a53b/s712_260305_P_P188499_Queen_Elizabeth_Memorial_DC04_View_17_Edited.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69aebe0cbde9c3f213c899ce/s465_260305_P_P188499_Queen_Elizabeth_Memorial_DC04_View_17_Edited.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69aebe0c6827004e30b8a539/260305_P_P188499_Queen_Elizabeth_Memorial_DC04_View_17_Edited.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-09T11:05:31.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Queen Elizabeth II served as Head of the Commonwealth for over 70 years. As the\nworld marks Commonwealth Day, we offer a first look at the landscape vision for her\nproposed memorial in St James’s Park - revealing gardens, and a sculpture by artist\nYinka Shonibare CBE that draws on her enduring relationship with the\nCommonwealth.</p>\n</div>","title":"A garden for the Commonwealth: the landscape vision for the Queen Elizabeth\r\nII Memorial"}],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"adhoc_advisory_group","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2024-01-15T12:53:02+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"AG1407","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/the-queen-elizabeth-memorial-committee","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/the-queen-elizabeth-memorial-committee","base_path":"/government/organisations/the-queen-elizabeth-memorial-committee","content_id":"1e4225ef-6beb-4d04-ab94-f9d9b39802d5","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-02-05T11:53:47Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"The Queen Elizabeth Memorial Committee","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-queen-elizabeth-memorial-committee","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_contacts":[{"content_id":"b904b67f-a4dc-41d0-92ff-9e7b6350ce79","details":{"contact_form_links":null,"description":null,"email_addresses":[{"email":"queenelizabethmemorial@cabinetoffice.gov.uk"}],"phone_numbers":null,"post_addresses":[],"title":"Contact us"},"document_type":"contact","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-10-21T12:13:03Z","schema_name":"contact","title":"Contact us","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D2